definition: variant of 夠嗆|够呛[gou4 qiang4]
enough (sufficient)/enough (too much)/(coll.) (before adj.) really/(coll.) to reach by stretching out
contrary/pushing against/bump/knock/used as equivalent for 搶|抢[qiang1]

sentences.english: My tooth is killing me. I can’t stand it.
sentences.chinese: 我的牙疼得夠戧，我真受不了了。
